    <item>
      <title>美国制裁放松后，中石油将接收委内瑞拉石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/petrochina-set-to-take-venezuelan-oil-after-us-sanctions-eased</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国去年底取消对欧佩克产油国的制裁后，中石油将接收一批委内瑞拉石油，这些石油将用于其位于广东的大型炼油厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/petrochina-set-to-take-venezuelan-oil-after-us-sanctions-eased</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:01:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油需求超出预期，测试原油峰值的计算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/oil-demand-outpaces-expectations-testing-calculus-on-peak-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球石油使用量比以往任何时候都多，今年的需求再次超出预期，引发了人们对全球消费何时达到峰值的疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/oil-demand-outpaces-expectations-testing-calculus-on-peak-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>双重上市计划削弱收购猜测，新秀丽股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/samsonite-slumps-as-dual-listing-plan-dents-buyout-interest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新秀丽国际公司 (Samsonite International SA) 的股价创下两年来最大跌幅，因为这家箱包制造商寻求第二次上市的计划损害了全球收购公司收购的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/samsonite-slumps-as-dual-listing-plan-dents-buyout-interest</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 01:49:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国平安表示盈利令人失望后将恢复利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/ping-an-profit-falls-unexpectedly-on-china-stock-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[平安保险（集团）股份有限公司预计盈利能力将恢复，全年净利润下降 23%，导致其股价创下 2022 年 11 月以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
